i18Ueditor.UeditorAboutUs:
Origin Data full name: Origin Data Global Limited.

 

Origin Data is a leading independent distributor of electronic components. Our primary focus is assisting customers in sourcing obsolete, end-of-life, hard-to-find and commonly used parts. Drawing on our extensive network and industry expertise, we provide timely, reliable quotes for hard-to-source electronic components and peripherals, ensuring fast delivery that our customers can rely on.

 

At Origin Data, our stores display millions of parts to meet the diverse needs of our loyal global OEM customer base. Our commitment to excellent customer service and market flexibility has earned us an excellent reputation in the industry.

 

One of our core strengths lies in our strict quality assurance (QA) system and professional quality control (QC) team. We work together to ensure that our products and services meet the highest quality standards. To further validate our commitment to quality, we are proud to be members of ERAI and hold certifications such as ESD, AS9120B, ISO9001, ISO14001 and more.

 

What sets us apart is our experienced staff who have deep industry knowledge and years of experience in the field. This allows us to work closely with our customers to understand their unique needs and provide tailor-made solutions.

 

At Origin Data, we strive to exceed our customers' expectations, provide exceptional service, and meet all of your electronic component needs.
i18Ueditor.ManufacturersDes: Origin Data Global Limited is a broad-line independent distributor of electronic components. We are dedicated to helping design engineers and procurement professionals easily select the products they need and find detailed information to help with the qualification process. If you can’t find what you are looking for, our product experts are only email away.
i18Ueditor.UeditorNotice:
Origin Data Global Limited 2024 National Day Holiday Notice


Dear Customers,


Thank you for your continued support of Origin Data Global Limited. In celebration of the 2024 National Day, we would like to inform you of our holiday schedule:


Holiday Schedule:


  • Holiday Dates: October 1, 2024 (Tuesday) to October 7, 2024 (Monday)

  • Normal Operations Resume: October 8, 2024 (Tuesday)

During this period, our website will remain open for orders. However, please be aware that order processing and customer service responses may experience some delays. We appreciate your understanding.


Wishing you a happy National Day and enjoyable shopping!


Origin Data Global Limited


Date: September 30, 2024
